msgctxt "1116"
msgid "Lost Homeless Man"
msgstr "Sin techo perdido"

msgctxt "1120"
msgid "Talk_Quest"
msgstr "Talk_Quest"

msgctxt "1124"
msgid "Wandering Homeless Man"
msgstr "Sin techo errante"

msgctxt "1128"
msgid "Talk_Think"
msgstr "Talk_Think"

msgctxt "84_Lost Homeless Man"
msgid "Huh? I thought the Millennium Tower was around here..."
msgstr "¿Eh? Pensé que la Torre Millennium estaba por aquí..."

msgctxt "96_Wandering Homeless Man"
msgid "Are we lost again? Come on... my feet are killing me."
msgstr "¿Nos hemos perdido de nuevo? Vamos... mis pies me están matando."

msgctxt "108_Lost Homeless Man"
msgid "I swear they said we just had to go this way, but..."
msgstr "Juro que dijeron que teníamos que ir por aquí, pero..."

msgctxt "120_Lost Homeless Man"
msgid "We somehow ended up in a subway tunnel, instead.\\r\n"
"Did we take a wrong turn somewhere?"
msgstr "En vez de eso, hemos acabado en un túnel del metro.\\r\n"
"¿Tomamos un giro equivocado en algún punto?"

msgctxt "132_Wandering Homeless Man"
msgid "Let's retrace our steps to that place under the theater\\r\n"
"and figure out where we got off track. Kamurocho's hard\\r\n"
"enough to navigate without getting lost beneath it."
msgstr "Deshagamos nuestros pasos hasta ese lugar bajo el teatro\\r\n"
"y averigüemos dónde nos desviamos del camino. Kamurocho\\r\n"
"ya es bastante complicada de navegar sin perderse debajo de ella."

